    "updated_at": "2016-02-05T11:01:09Z",
    "body": "I can verify that the dependency _is_ added into the bundle by browserify. I can test this as follows:\n\n```\nvar launcher = require('browser-launcher2'); //Browserify parses this require, adds to bundle\nvar remoteLauncher = remote.require('browser-launcher2'); //Fails, it's not on the local filesystem\n```\n"
