    "updated_at": "2016-02-05T12:57:31Z",
    "body": "Ah silly me, in order for Browserify to load modules from a bundle it would have to provide it's own `require()`, but it won't be able to hijack `remote.require()`. So you'll have to require it in the main process instead and expose the API via IPC.\n"
