    "updated_at": "2016-02-05T13:36:35Z",
    "body": "`remote.require()` calls `process.mainModule.require()` in the main process, you could perhaps monkey-patch `process.mainModule.require()` to call Browserify's `require` if the default implementation fails to load the requested module.\n"
